snippet: Israel on Saturday killed a senior Palestinian militant and his assistant in an airstrike in the northern Gaza Strip, a spokesman for the Gaza medical services said.

byline.contributor: Isabel Kershner contributed reporting from Jerusalem.

lead_paragraph: Israel on Saturday killed a senior Palestinian militant and his assistant in an airstrike in the northern Gaza Strip, a spokesman for the Gaza medical services said.

headline.seo: Israeli Airstrike Kills Palestinian Militants in Gaza
headline.main: Israeli Airstrike Kills 2 Militants in Gaza
